hadiths[139]{hadithnumber,text}:
1897,"mainey arz kiya Allah key Rasool ! main kis key sath nek sulook aur sila rehmi karun? aap ney farmaya : ''apni maa key sath'' ,mainey arz kiya : phir kis key sath ? farmaya : ''apni maa key sath'' , mainey arz kiya : phir kis key sath? farmaya : ''apni maa key sath'' , mainey arz kiya : phir kis key sath? farmaya : ''phir apney baap key sat , phir rishte daaron key sath phir sab sey ziyada qaribi rishte daar phir uskey baad ka, darja badarja.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, Shoba ney Behaz bin Hakeem key barey mein kalam kiya hai, muhaddeseen key nazdik wo bharosemand hain, in sey Maamar , Sory , Hammad bin Salma aur kaee Aaimmae hadees ney riwayat ki hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Abdullah bin Amr , Aaisha aur Abu-Darda (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1898,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha : Allah key Rasool ! kon sa amal sab sey afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : '' waqt par namaz ada karna '' , mainey puchha : Allah key Rasool ! phir kon sa amal ziyada behtar hai? aap ney farmaya : '' maa baap key sath husne-suluk karna '' , mainey puchha : Allah key Rasool ! phir kon sa amal ? aap ney farmaya : '' Allah ki raah mein jihad karna '' , phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khamosh ho gaey, halanke agar main ziyada poochhta to aap ziyada batatey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isey abu-Amr Shebaani, Shoba aur kaee logon ney Waleed bin Eizaar sey riwayat ki hai. 3- ye hadees abu-Amr Shebaani key wastey sey ibne-Masood sey dusri sanadon sey bhi aai hai."
1899,"eik aadmi ney unkey paas aa kar kaha : meri eik biwi hai, aur meri maa us ko Talaq deney ka hukm deti hai, ( main kya karun ? ( Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : '' baap jannat ka darmiyani darwaza hai, agar tum chaho to us darwaza ko zaya kar do aur chaho to uski hifazat karo.''  Sufiyan bin Uena ney kabhi « un ummi » ( meri maa ( kaha aur kabhi « un ubai » ( mera baap ( kaha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
1900,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Rab ki raza walid ki raza mein hai aur Rab ki naaraazagi walid ki naaraazagi mein hai.''
1901,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kya main tum logon ko sab sey badey gunah key barey mein na bata dun? Sahaba ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kyon nahin ? aap ney farmaya : '' Allah key sath shirk karna aur maa baap ki nafarmani karna '' , Raavi kehtey hain : aap uth bethey halanke aap tek lagaey huye they, phir farmaya : '' aur jhooti gawahi dena '' , ya jhooti baat kehna Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam baar-baar usey dohraatey rahey yahan tak ke hamney kaha : '' kaash! aap khamosh ho jatey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1902,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''apney maa baap ko gaali dena kabeera gunahon mein sey hai'' , Sahaba ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! bhala koi aadmi apney maa baap ko bhi gaali dega ? aap ney farmaya : '' haan , wo kisi key baap ko gaali dega , to wo bhi uskey baap ko gaali dega, aur wo kisi ki maa ko gaali dega, to wo bhi uski maa ko gaali dega''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1903,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : '' sab sey behtar sulook aur sab sey achcha bartaaw ye hai ke aadmi apney baap key doston key sath sila-rehmi kerey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye sanad sahih hai, ye hadees ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey kaee sanadon sey aai hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1904,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''khaala maa key darjey mein hai'', is hadees main eik lamba qissa hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
1905,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''teen duayen maqbool hoti hain, un mein koi shak nahin hai : mazloom ki dua, musafir ki dua aur betey key ooper baap ki bad-dua''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Hujjaaj Sawaaf ney bhi Yahya bin abi Kasir sey Hisham ki hadees jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai, abu Jaafar jinhoney Abu-Hurera sey riwayat ki hai unhen abu Jaafar muazzan kaha jata hai, hum unka naam nahin jantey hain, 2- un sey Yahya bin abi Kasir ney kaee hadisein riwayat ki hain."
1906,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' koi ladka apney baap ka ehsan nahin chuka sakta hai siwaye uskey ke usey ( yani baap ko) ghulam paey aur kharid kar azad kar dey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai, hum isey sirf Suhel bin abi Saleh ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 3- Sufiyan Sory aur kaee logon ney bhi ye hadees Suhel bin abi Saleh sey riwayat ki hai."
1907,"Abu-Raddad Leisi bimar ho gaey, Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) un ki iyaadat ko gaey, unhoney kaha : merey ilm key mutabiq abu Muhammad ( Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ( logon mein sab sey achey aur sila rehmi karney waley hain, Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : '' Allah tabarak w taala ney farmaya : main Allah hun, main Rehman hun, mainey « reham » ( yani rishtey natey ( ko paida kya hai, aur uska naam apney naam sey (nikal kar) rakha hai, isliye jo usey jodeyga mein usey ( apni rehmat sey) jodey rakhunga aur jo usey kaatega main bhi usey (apni rehmat sey) kaat dunga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein abu Saeed Khudri, ibne-Abi Aufi, Aamir bin Rabeea, Abu-Hurera aur Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 2- Zohri sey marvi Sufiyan ki hadees sahih hai, Maamar ney Zohri sey ye hadees (عن أبي سلمة an رداد الليثي an عبدالرحمٰن بن عوف و معمر) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai, Maamar ney (sanad bayan kartey huye) aisa hi kaha hai, Muhammad (Bukhari) kehtey hain : Maamar ki hadees mein khata hai, (dono sanadon mein farq wazeh hai)."
1908,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' sila rehmi karney wala wo nahin hai jo badla chukaaey, balke haqeeqi sila rehmi karney wala wo hai jo rishtey natey todney par bhi sila rehmi karey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Salman , Aaisha aur Abdullah bin umr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1909,Juber bin Mut-im (rz) kehtey hain ke Rasoolullah ney farmaya : rishta naata wala jannat mein dakhil nahin hoga. ibne-Abi umr kahtey hain : Sufiyan ney kaha : قاطع sey murad rishta naata todney wala hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1910,"eik din Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam god main apni beti ( Fatima ( key do ladkon ( Hasan , Husain) mein sey kisi ko liye huye bahar nikley aur aap (us ladkey ki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar) farma rahey they : '' tum log bakheel bana detey ho, tum log buzdil bana detey ho, aur tum log jahil bana detey ho, yaqinan tum log Allah key ata kiye huye phoolon mein sey ho''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ibrahim bin Maisra sey marvi ibn Uena ki hadees ko hum sirf unhi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- hum nahin jantey hain ke umr bin abdul-Azeez ka samaa, khaula sey Sabit hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein ibne-Umar aur Ash-as bin Qais (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1911,"Hazrat Ibne-Umar, Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman Sufiyan, Zohri, abu-Salma, Hazrat Abu-Hurera ( رض ( riwayat hai ke wo farmatey hain ke Aqraa bin Habis ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu alehi w-aalehi wasallam) ko Hazrat Hasan ka bosa letey huye dekha ibne-Abi umr apni bayan karda mein Hasan ya Husain ka zikr kartey hain pas Aqraa ney kaha merey das betey hain mainey kabhi unka bosa nahin liya. aap ney farmaya jo reham nahin karta is par reham nahin kya jata. is baab mein Hazrat Anas aur Aaisha sey bhi ahadees manqul hain. abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ka naam Abdullah hai ye hadees Hasan sahih hai"
1912,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum mein sey kisi key paas teen ladkiyan ya teen behney hon aur wo unkey sath achcha sulook karey to jannat mein zarur dakhil hoga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu Saeed Khudri ka naam Saad bin Malik bin Sanan hai, aur Saad bin abi Waqas ka naam Saad bin Malik bin Wuheb hai, 2- is hadees ki dusri sanad mein raawiyon ney ( Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman aur abu-Saeed key darmiyan (eik aur Raavi ( Ayub bin Bashir (ka izafa kya hai, 3- is bab mein Aaisha , Aqba bin Aamir , Anas , Jabir aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1913,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs ladkiyon ki parwarish sey do-chaar ho, phir unki parwarish sey aaney wali musibaton par sabr karey to ye sab ladkiyan uskey liye jahannam sey aad banengi''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
1914,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney do ladkiyon ki kafalat ki to main aur wo jannat mein is tarah dakhil hongey '', aur aap ney keyfiyat bataaney key liye apni dono ungliyon (shahadat aur darmiyani) sey ishara kya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, 2- Muhammad bin Ubaid ney Muhammad bin abdul-Azeez key wastey sey isi sanad sey kaee hadisein riwayat ki hai aur sanad bayan kartey huye kaha hai : (عن أبي بكر بن عبيد الله بن أنس) halanke sahih yun hai (عن عبيد الله بن أبي بكر بن أنس)"
1915,"merey paas eik aurat aai aur uskey sath uski do bachchiyan thin, usney ( khaney key liye ( koi chiz maangi magar merey paas sey eik khajoor key siwa usey kuch nahin mila , chunanche usey mainey wohi dey diya, us aurat ney khajoor ko khud na kha kar usey apni dono ladkiyon key darmiyan baant diya aur uth kar chali gaee , phir merey paas Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tashrif laye, mainey aap sey ye ( waqia ( bayan kya to aap ney farmaya : '' jo un ladkiyon ki parwarish sey do chaar ho uskey liye ye sab jahannam sey parda hongi '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1916,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jis key paas teen ladkiyan , ya teen behneein, ya do ladkiyan, ya do behnein hon aur wo unkey sath achcha sulook karey aur unkey huquq key silsiley mein Allah sey darey to uskey liye jannat hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai۔"
1917,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs kisi musalman yatim ko apney sath rakh kar unhen khilaaey palaey , to bilashuba Allah Taala usey jannat mein dakhil kerega, siwaye uskey ke wo aisa gunah ( shirk ( karey jo maghfirat key qabil na ho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Raavi hansh ka naam Husain bin Qais hai, kunniyat abu-Ali Rahbi hai, Suleman (Alaihissalam) Temi kehtey hain : ye muhaddeseen key nazdik zaeef hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein Murra Fahri, abu-Huraira, abu-Umama aur Sehal bin Saad (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1918,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main aur yatim ki kafalat karney wala jannat mein in dono ki tarah hongey padhi. aur aap ney apni shahadat aur darmiyani ungli ki taraf ishara kya ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1919,"eik boodha aaya , wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey milna chahta tha, logon ney usey raasta deney mein der ki to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' wo shakhs hum mein sey nahin hai, jo hamarey chhoton par meharbani na karey aur hamarey badon ki izzat na kerey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- Raavi Zarbi ney Anas bin Malik aur doosrey logon sey kaee munkar hadisein riwayat ki hain, padhi. 3- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr , Abu-Hurera , ibne-Abbas aur abu-Umama (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1920,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' wo shakhs hum mein sey nahin hai jo hamarey chhoton par meharbani na karey aur hamarey badon ka maqam na pehchaney ''.
1921,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''wo shakhs hum mein sey nahin hai jo hamarey chhoton par meharbani na karey aur hamarey badon ki izzat na karey, maroof (bhali baaton) ka hukm na dey aur munkir ( buri baaton ( sey mana na karey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Muhammad bin Is-haq ki Amr bin Shuaib key wastey sey marvi (riwayat hui) hadees sahih hai. 3- Abdullah bin Amr sey ye hadees dusri sanadon sey bhi aai hai. 4- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key is qol (ليس منا) ka mafhoom ye hai (ليس من سنتنا ليس من أدبنا) yani wo hamarey taur tareeqe par nahin hai. 5- Ali bin Madini kehtey hain : Yahya bin Saeed ney kaha : Sufiyan Sory is tafseer ki tardeed (inkaar) kartey they aur is ka mafhoom ye bayan kartey they ke (ليس منا) sey murad (ليس من ملتنا) hai, yani wo hamari millat ka nahin hai."
1922,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs logon par meharbani nahin karta Allah Taala is par meharbani nahin kerega.''Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai,.  2- is bab mein Abdur-Rehman bin Auf , abu Saeed Khudri , ibne-Umar , Abu-Hurera aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1923,"mainey Abul-Qaasim Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''sirf bad-bakht hi (key dil) sey reham khatam kiya jata hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- abu-Usman jinhoney Abu-Hurera sey ye hadees riwayat ki hai unka naam nahin malum hai, kaha jata hai, wo us Musa bin abu-Usman key walid hain jin sey abu-Zinad ney riwayat ki hai, abu-Zinad ney (an Musa bin abi Usman an Abeeh an abi Huraira an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) ki sanad sey kaee hadisein riwayat ki hain."
1924,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''reham karney walon par Rehman reham karta hai, tum log zamin walon par reham karo tum par aasman wala reham kerega, reham Rehman sey nikla hai, jisney is ko joda Allah us ko (apni rehmat sey) jodeyga aur jisney is ko toda Allah us ko apni rehmat sey kaat dega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1925,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey namaz qaaim karney , zakat deney aur har musalman key sath khair-khahi karney par baiat ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1926,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney teen martaba farmaya : ''deen sarapa khair-khahi hai.'' , logon ney puchha : Allah key Rasool ! kis key liye? farmaya : ''Allah key liye, uski kitab key liye, musalmanon key Aaimma (hukmranon) aur aam musalmanon key liye.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , Tameem daari , Jareer , (Hakeem bin abi Yazeed an Abeeh) aur Soban (Raziallauh anhum) sey ahadees aai hain."
1927,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''eik musalman doosrey musalman ka bhai hai, uskey sath khayanat na kerey. us sey jhoot na boley , aur us ko beyaar aur madadgar na chhodey, har musalman ki izzat , dolat aur khoon doosrey musalman key liye haram hai, taqwa yahan (dil mein) hai, eik shakhs key bura honey key liye yehi kafi hai ke wo apney kisi musalman bhai ko haqeer aur kamtar samjhey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Ali aur abu-Ayyub Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1928,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''eik momin doosrey momin key liye imarat ki tarah hai, jis ka eik hissa doosrey hissey ko mazbut karta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1929,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum mein sey har aadmi apney bhai key liye aaeina hai, agar wo apney bhai key andar koi aeb dekhey to usey (ittilaa key zarie) door kar dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Shoba ney Yahya bin Ubedullah ko zaeef kaha hai. 2- is bab mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1930,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney kisi musalman ki koi duniyaawi takleef door ki, Allah Taala uski qiyamat ki takleefon mein sey koi takleef door farma dega, jisney duniya mein kisi tang dast key sath aasani ki Allah Taala uskey sath duniya aur aakhirat dono mein aasani kerega, aur jisney duniya mein kisi musalman key aeb ki parda poshi ki Allah Taala duniya aur aakhirat mein uskey aeb ki parda poshi kerega, jab tak banda apney bhai ki madad mein laga rehta hai Allah Taala uski madad mein hota hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- is hadees ko abu Awaana aur kaee logon ney (an Aamash an abi Saleh an abi Huraira an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam ki sanad sey isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai, lekin is mein (an abi Saleh) key alfaz nahin bayan kiye hain. 3- is bab mein ibne-Umar aur Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1931,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney bhai ki izzat (uski ghair mojudgi mein) bachaey Allah Taala qiyamat key din uskey chehrey ko jahannam sey bachaeyga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Asma binte Yazeed (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1932,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kisi musalman key liye jayez nahin ke apney ( kisi doosrey musalman ( bhai sey teen din sey ziyada salam kalam band rakhey , jab dono ka aamna samna ho to wo us sey munh pher ley aur ye us sey munh pher ley , aur in dono mein behtar wo hai jo pehley salam kerey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Masood , Anas , Abu-Hurera , Hisham bin Aamir aur Abu Hind Daari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1933,"jab Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) (hijrat kar key) Madina aaye to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unkey aur Saad bin Rabee key darmiyan bhai chaara qaaim kiya, Saad bin Rabee ney Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : aaoo tumharey liye apna aadha maal baant dun, aur merey paas do biwiyan hain un mein sey eik ko Talaq dey deta hun, jab uski iddat guzar jaey to us sey shaadi kar lo, Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah Taala tumharey maal aur tumhari aulad mein barkat dey, mujhey bazar ka raasta bataao, unhoney in ko bazar ka raasta bata diya, us din wo (baazaar sey) kuchh paneer aur ghi ley kar hi lotey jo nafe mein unhen hasil huwa tha, iskey (kuchh dino) baad Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unkey ooper zardi ka asar dekha to puchha : kya baat hai? ''(ye zardi kaisi) kaha : mainey eik Ansari aurat sey shaadi ki hai, aap ney puchha : ''us ko mehar main tum ney kya diya?'' kaha : eik (soney ki) guthli, (ya guthli key barabar sona) aap ney farmaya : ''waleema karo agar-che eik bakri hi ka ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Ahmed kehtey hain : guthli key barabar sona sawa teen dirham key barabar hota hai. 3- Is-haq bin Ibrahim bin Raahviya kehtey hain : guthli key barabar sona , paanch dirham key barabar hota hai."
1934,"kisi ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! gheebat kya hai? aap ney farmaya : ''us andaz sey apney bhai ka tumhara zikr karna jisey wo napasand karey.'' , usney kaha : aap ka kya khayal hai agar wo chiz is mein mojud ho jisey main bayan kar raha hun? aap ney farmaya : ''jo tum bayan kar rahey ho agar wo is mein mojud hai to tum ney uski gheebat (chughli) ki, aur jo tum bayan kar rahey ho agar wo is mein mojud nahin hai to tum ney is par tohmat baandhi.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Barza , ibne-Umar aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1935,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aapas mein qata' talluq na karo, eik doosrey sey berukhi na ikhtiyar karo, baham (aapas mein) dushmani aur bughz na rakho, eik doosrey sey hasad na karo, Allah key bando ! aapas mein bhai bhai bin jaao, kisi musalman key liye jayez nahin ke teen din sey ziyada apney musalman bhai sey salam kalam band rakhey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Bakar Siddiq, Zuber bin Awam , ibne-Masood aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1936,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sirf do aadmiyon par rashk karna chahiye, eik us aadmi par jis ko Allah Taala ney maal diya aur wo is mein sey raat din (Allah ki raah mein) kharch karta hai, doosra us aadmi par jis ko Allah Taala ney ilme Quran diya aur wo raat din uska haq ada karta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ibne-Masood aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma key wastey sey bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah ki hadees aai hai."
1937,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''shetan is baat sey mayus ho chuka hai ke namazi uski ibadat karengey, lekin wo unkey darmiyan jhagda karaney ki koshish mein rehta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Anas aur (Suleman bin Amr bin Al Ahwas an Abeeh) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1938,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''wo shakhs jhoota nahin hai jo logon key darmiyan suleh kiraaey aur wo ( khud eik taraf sey doosrey key barey mein) achchhi baat kahey , ya achchhi baat badha kar bayan karey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1939,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sirf teen jagah par jhoot jayez aur halal hai, eik ye ke aadmi apni biwi sey baat karey taake us ko razi kar ley, doosra jang mein jhoot bolnaa aur teesra logon key darmiyan suleh karaney key liye jhoot bolnaa.''"
1940,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo doosrey ko nuqsan pahunchaey Allah usey nuqsan pahunchaeyga aur jo doosrey ko takleef dey Allah Taala usey takleef dega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Bakar sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1941,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''wo shakhs mal'oon  yani Allah ki rehmat sey door) hai jisney kisi momin ko nuqsan pahunchaya ya us ko dhoka diya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai.
1942,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mujhey Jibreel (Alaihissalam) padoshi key sath husne-suluk karney ki hamesha wasiyat ( takeed ( kartey rahey , yahan tak ke mujhey guman honey laga ke ye usey virasat mein) bhi) shareek thehra dengey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1943,"Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas Raziallahu anhuma key liye unkey ghar main eik bakri zibeh ki gaee , jab wo aaye to puchha : kya tum logon ney hamarey Yahudi padosi key ghar (gosht ka ( hadiya bheja? kya tum logon ney hamarey Yahudi padosi key ghar hadiya bheja hai? mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : mujhey Jibreel (Alaihissalam) padosi key sath husne-suluk karney ki hamesha takeed kartey rahey yahan tak ke mujhey guman honey laga ke ye usey waris bana dengey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye hadees Mujahid sey Aaisha aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma key wastey sey bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , ibne-Abbas , Abu-Hurera , Anas , Miqdaad bin Aswad , Aqba bin Aamir , abu-Shuraih aur abu-Umama (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1944,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah key nazdik sab sey behtar dost wo hai jo logon mein apney dost key liye behtar hai, aur Allah key nazdik sab sey behtar padosi wo hai jo apney padosi key liye behtar hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
1945,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tumharey khaadim tumharey bhai hain, Allah Taala ney in ko tumharey matahat kar diya hai, lihaza jis key tehat mein uska bhai ( khaadim (ho , wo usey apney khaaney mein sey khilaaey , apney kapdon mein sey pahnaaey aur usey kisi aisey kaam ka mukallaf na banaey jo usey aajiz kar dey, aur agar usey kisi aisey kaam ka mukallaf banata hai, jo usey aajiz kar dey to uski madad karey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , Umme-Salma , ibne-Umar aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1946,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''wo shakhs jannat mein dakhil nahin hoga jo khaadimon key sath bura sulook karta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- Ayub Sakhtiyaan aur kaee logon ney Raavi Farqad Sabkhi key barey mein unkey haafzey key talluq sey kalam kiya hai.
1947,"Nabi Tauba abul-Qaasim Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney ghulam ya laundi par zina ki tohmat lagaey halanke wo uski tohmat sey bari hai to Allah Taala qiyamat key din is par had qaaim kerega, illa ye ke wo wesa hi Sabit ho jaisa usney kaha tha ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Suwed bin Muqrin aur Abdullah bin umr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1948,"main apney ghulam ko maar raha tha ke peechey sey kisi kehney waley ki aawaz suni wo keh raha tha : abu-Masood jaan lo, abu-Masood jaan lo ( yani khabrdar ( , jab mainey mud kar dekha to merey paas Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam they aap ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala tum par us sey kahin ziyada qadir hai jitna ke tum us ghulam par qadir ho ''. abu-Masood kehtey hain : uskey baad mainey apney kisi ghulam ko nahin maara padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1949,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik aadmi ney aa kar puchha : Allah key Rasool ! main apney khaadim ki ghaltiyon ko kitni baar maaf karun? aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam us shakhs key us sawal par khamosh rahey , usney phir puchha : Allah key Rasool ! main apney khaadim ki ghaltiyon ko kitni baar maaf karun ? aap ney farmaya : ''har din sattar baar maaf karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- isey Abdullah bin Wahab ney bhi abu-Haani Khaulaani sey isi tarah riwayat kiya hai."
1950,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey koi apney khaadim ko maarey aur wo (khaadim) Allah ka naam ley ley to tum apney haathon ko rok lo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Raavi Abu Haarun Abdi ka naam Umaara bin Juwain hai, abu-Bakar Attaar ney Yahya bin Saeed ka ye qol naqal kiya ke Shoba ney Abu Haarun Abdi ki tazeef (zaeef maana) ki hai, Yahya kehtey hain : ibne Aun hamesha Abu Haarun sey riwayat kartey rahey yahan tak ke un ki wafat ho gaee."
1951,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''apney ladkey ko adab sikhaana eik saa sadqa deney sey behtar hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- Raavi Naasah ki kunniyat Abul Alaa hai, aur ye koofa key rehney waley hain, muhaddeseen key nazdik qawi nahin hain, ye hadees sirf isi sanad sey maroof hai. 3- Naasah eik doosrey Shaikh bhi hain jo Basra key rehney waley hain, Ammar bin Abu Ammar waghera sey hadees riwayat kartey hain, aur ye un sey ziyada qawi hain."
1952,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Hasan adab sey behtar kisi baap ney apney betey ko tohfa nahin diya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Aamir bin Abu-Aamir Khazzaaz ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur Aamir Saleh bin Rustam Khazzaaz key betey hain. 2- Raavi Ayub bin Musa sey murad Ayub bin Musa bin Amr bin Saeed bin Aas hain. 3- ye hadees merey nazdik mursal hai."
1953,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hadiya qubul kartey they aur uska badla detey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib sahih hai. 2- hum isey sirf Esa bin Yunus ki riwayat sey jantey hain, jisey wo Hisham sey riwayat kartey hain. 3- is bab mein Abu-Huraira, Anas, ibne-Umar aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1954,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo logon ka shukariya ada na karey wo Allah ka shukar ada nahin kerega.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1955,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney logon ka shukariya ada na kiya usney Allah ka shukar ada nahin kiya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Huraira, Ash-as bin Qais aur Noman bin Bashir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1956,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''apney bhai key samney tumhara muskarana tumharey liye sadqa hai, tumhara bhalai ka hukm dena aur burai sey rokna sadqa hai, bhatak janey wali jagah mein kisi aadmi ko tumhara raasta dikhaana tumharey liye sadqa hai, na-bina aur kam dekhney waley aadmi ko raasta dikhaana tumharey liye sadqa hai, patthar , kaanta aur haddi ko raastey sey hataanaa tumharey liye sadqa hai, apney dol sey apney bhai key dol main tumhara pani dalna tumharey liye sadqa hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood , Jabir , Huzefa , Aaisha aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey ahadees aai hain."
1957,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : '' jis shakhs ney doodh ka Atiya diya padhi. , ya chaandi qarz di, ya kisi ko raasta bataya , usey ghulam azad karney key barabar sawab milega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Abu-Is'haq ki riwayat sey jisey wo Talha bin Musrif sey riwayat kartey hain Hasan sahih gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Mansoor bin Moa'tamir aur Shoba ney bhi is hadees ki riwayat Talha bin Musrif sey ki hai. 3- is bab mein Noman bin Bashir Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadees aai hai. 4- (من منح منيحة ورق) ka matlab hai bator qarz dena (هدى زقاقا) ka matlab hai raasta dikhaanaa."
1958,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' eik aadmi raastey par chal raha tha ke usey eik kaantay daar dali mili , usney isey raastey sey hata diya, Allah Taala ney uskey is kaam sey khush ho kar us ko badla diya yani uski maghfirat farma di.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Barza , ibne-Abbas aur Abu-Zar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1959,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab koi aadmi tum sey koi baat bayan karey phir ( usey raz mein rakhney key liye ( daain baain mud kar dekhey to wo baat tumharey paas amanat hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- hum isey sirf ibne-Abi Zi-ib ki riwayat sey jantey hain.
1960,"mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! merey ghar mein sirf Zuber ki kamai hai, kya main is mein sey sadqa aur khairat karun? aap ney farmaya : ''haan, sadqa karo aur gireh mat lagaao warna tumharey ooper gireh laga di jaeygi.''  (لا توكي فيوكى عليك) ka matlab ye hai ke shumar kar key sadqa na karo warna Allah Taala bhi shumar kerega aur barkat khatam kar dega. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- baaz raawiyon ney is hadees ko :(عن ابن أبي مليكة an عباد بن عبد الله بن الزبير an أسماء بنت أبي بكر رضي الله عنهما) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai padhi. , kaee logon ney is hadees ki riwayat Ayub sey ki hai aur is mein Ibaad bin Ubedullah bin Zuber ka zikr nahin kiya. 2- is bab mein Aaisha aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1961,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sakhi aadmi Allah sey qarib hai, jannat sey qarib hai, logon sey qarib hai aur jahannam sey door hai, bakheel aadmi Allah sey door hai, jannat sey door hai, logon sey door hai, aur jahannam sey qarib hai, jahil sakhi Allah key nazdik bakheel abid sey kahin ziyada mehbub hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey (Yahya bin Saeed an Al Aaraj an abi Huraia) ki sanad sey sirf Saad bin Muhammad ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur Yahya bin Saeed sey is hadees ki riwayat karney mein Saeed bin Muhammad ki mukhalifat ki gaee hai, ( Saeed bin Muhammad ney to is sanad sey riwayat ki hai jo ooper mazkur (zikr hui) hai) jabke ye (an Yahya bin Saeed an Aaysha) ki sanad sey bhi mursalan marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
1962,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''momin key andar do khaslatein bukhl (kanjusi) aur badakhlaaqi jama nahin ho saktin.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Sadqa bin Musa ki riwayat sey hi jantey hain. padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1963,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''dhoke-baaz, ehsan jataney wala aur bakheel (kanjus) jannat mein nahin dakhil hongey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
1964,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''momin bholaa-bhaala aur shareef hota hai, aur faajir dhoke baaz aur kamina khaslat hota hai.''"
1965,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aadmi ka apney baal bachchon par kharch karna sadqa hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr , Amr bin Umayya Zamri aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1966,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sab sey behtar Dinar wo Dinar hai, jisey aadmi apney ehal aur ayaal par kharch karta hai, aur wo Dinar hai jisey aadmi apney jihad ki sawari par kharch karta hai, aur wo Dinar hai jisey aadmi apney Mujahid sathiyon par kharch karta hai.''  Abu-Qulaba kehtey hain : aap ney baal-bachhon key nafqa (akhrajaat) sey shuruaat ki phir farmaya : ''us aadmi sey bada ajr aur sawab wala kon hai jo apney chhotey bachchon par kharch karta hai, jin key zariey Allah Taala unhen haram chizon sey bachata hai aur unhen maaldaar banata hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1967,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ye hadees bayan farma rahey they to meri aakhon ney aap ko dekha aur kanon ney aap sey suna , aap ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta hai wo apney mehman ki izzat kartey huye uska haq ada kerey.''  Sahaba ney arz kiya, mehman ki izzat ayr takrim aur Aaw-bhugat kiya hai? padhi. aap ney farmaya : ''eik din aur eik raat , aur mehman nawaazi teen din tak hai aur jo iskey baad ho wo sadqa hai, jo shakhs Allah aur  aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho, wo achchhi baat kahey ya khamosh rahey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1968,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ziyaafat (mehman nawaazi) teen Deen tak hai, aur mehman ka Atiya (yani uskey liye takalluf ke saath khaney ka intizam karna) eik din aur eik raat tak hai, uskey baad jo kuchh is par kharch kiya jaeyga wo sadqa hai, mehman key liye jayez nahin ke mezban key paas (teen din key baad bhi) thehra rahey jis sey apney mezban ko pareshani aur mashaqqat mein dal dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Malik bin Anas aur Les bin Saad ney is hadees ki riwayat Saeed Maqbari sey ki hai. 3- abu-Shuraih Khuzai ki nisbat Kaa'bi aur Advi hai, aur unka naam Khuwelid bin Amr hai. 4- is bab mein Aaisha aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 5- (لا يثوي عنده) ka matlab ye hai ke mehman ghar waley key paas thehra na rahey taake is par giraan guzrey. 6- (الحرج) ka maana (الضيق) (tangi hai) aur (حتى يحرجه) ka matlab hai (يضيق عليه) yahan tak ke wo usey pareshani aur mashaqqat mein dal dey."
1969,"Aap ney farmaya : ''bewa aur miskeen par kharch karney wala Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley ki tarah hai, ya us aadmi ki tarah hai jo din mein roza rakhta hai aur raat mein ibadat karta hai."
1970,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''har bhalai sadqa hai, aur bhalai ye bhi hai ke tum apney bhai sey khush mizaaji key sath milo aur apney dol sey uskey dol mein pani dal do.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1971,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sach bolo, isliye ke sach neki ki taraf rehnumai karta hai aur neki jannat ki taraf rehnumai karti hai, aadmi hamesha sach boltaa hai aur sach ki talash mein rehta hai, yahan tak ke wo Allah key nazdik sachcha likh diya jata hai, aur jhoot sey bacho, isliye ke jhoot gunah ki taraf rehnumai karta hai aur gunah jahannam mein ley jata hai, aadmi hamesha jhoot boltaa hai aur jhoot ki talash mein rehta hai yahan tak ke Allah key nazdik jhoota likh diya jata hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Bakar Siddiq , umr , Abdullah bin Shikhkhir aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1972,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab banda jhoot boltaa hai to us jhoot ki badboo ki wajeh sey farishta us sey eik mail door bhaagtaa hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. Yahya bin Musa kehtey hain : mainey Abdur-Raheem bin Harun sey puchha : kya aap sey Abdul-Azeez bin Abi Dawud ney ye hadees bayan ki? kaha : haan. 2- hum isey sirf isi tareeq sey jantey hain, iski riwayat karney mein Abdur-Raheem bin Harun munfarid (bilkul alag) hain."
1973,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key nazdik jhoot sey badh kar koi aur aadat nafrat key qabil naa-pasandida nahin thi, aur jab koi aadmi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas jhoot boltaa to wo hamesha aap ki nazar mein qabile-nafrat rehta yahan tak ke aap jaan letey ke usney jhoot sey tauba kar li hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
1974,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis chiz mein bhi behayaae aati hai usey aeb daar kar deti hai aur jis chiz mein hayaa aati hai usey zeenat bakhshti hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Abdur-Razzaaq ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- is bab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1975,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum mein sab sey behtar wo log hain jo akhlaq mein behtar hain, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam behayaa aur bad-zabaan nahin they.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1976,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum log (kisi par) Allah ki lanat na bhejo, na uskey ghazab ki lanat bhejo aur na jahannam ki lanat bhejo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , Abu-Hurera , ibne-Umar aur Imran bin Husain (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1977,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''momin taana deney wala , lanat karney wala , behayaa aur bad-zabaan nahin hota hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye hadees Abdullah sey dusri sanad sey bhi aai hai."
1978,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney eik aadmi ney hawa par lanat bheji to aap ney farmaya : ''hawa par lanat na bhejo isliye ke wo to ( Allah key ( hukm ki paband hai, aur jis shakhs ney kisi aisi chiz par lanat bheji jo lanat ki mustahiq nahin hai to lanat usi par lot aati hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Bishr bin umr key ilawa hum kisi ko nahin jantey jisney isey marfooan bayan kiya hai."
1979,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''is qadr apna nasab jano jis sey tum apney rishtey jod sako, isliye ke rishta jodney sey rishte-daaron ki mohabbat badhti hai, maal aur dolat mein izafa hota hai, aur aadmi ki umr badha di jati hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai. 2- « منسأة في الأثر » ka matlab hai « الزيادة في العمر » yani umr key lambi honey ka sabab hai."
1980,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''koi dua itni jald qubul nahin hoti hai jitni jald ghaaieb aadmi key haq mein ghaaieb aadmi ki dua qubul hoti hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Raavi Afriqi hadees key silsiley mein zaeef qarar diye gaey hain, unka naam Abdur-Rehman bin Ziyad bin Anam hai."
1981,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''gaalii galoch karney waley do aadmiyon mein sey gaali ka gunah un mein sey shuru karney waley par hoga, jab tak mazloom had sey aagey na badh jaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Saad , ibne-Masood aur Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadisein marvi (riwayat hui) hain."
1982,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mardon ko gaali dey kar zindon ko takleef na pohchaao.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is hadees ki riwayat karney mein Sufiyan key shagrid mukhtalif hain, baaz ney Hafri ki hadees key jasi riwayat ki hai (yani : "" عن زياد بن علاقة ، an المغيرة"" key tareeq sey) aur baaz ney isey :(عن سفيان an زياد بن علاقة قال سمعت رجلا يحدث عند المغيرة بن شعبة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai."
1983,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''musalman ko gaali dena fisq (nafarmaani) hai aur us sey jhagda karna kufr hai.''  Raavi Zubeda bin Haris kehtey hain : mainey abu-Waeil Shaqeeq bin Salma sey puchha : kya aap ney ye hadees Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey suni hai? kaha : haan. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1984,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jannat mein aisey bala-khaney hain jinke berooni (baahiri) hissey andar sey aur andruni hissey bahar sey nazar aayege.''  (ye sun kar) eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ney khadey ho kar arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! kis key liye hain? aap ney farmaya : ''jo achchhi tarah baat karey , khana khilaaey , khub roza rakhey aur Allah ki raza key liye raat mein namaz padhey jabke log soey hon.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Abdur-Rehman bin Is-haq ki riwayat sey jantey hain, Is-haq bin Abdur-Rehman key haafze key talluq sey baaz muhaddeseen ney kalam kiya hai, ye koofa key rehney waley hain. 3- Abdur-Rehman bin Is-haq naam key eik doosrey Raavi hain, wo qarshi aur Madina key rehney waley hain, ye un sey asbat hain, aur dono key dono ek hi zamaane ke hain."
1985,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''un key liye kya hi achchha hai ke apney rab ki itaat karen aur apney Malik ka haq ada karen.''  aap key is farman ka matlab laundi aur ghulam sey tha. Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : Allah aur uskey Rasool ney sach farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Musa Ash-ari aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain.
1986,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''teen aadmi mushk key tiley par hongey, qiyamat key din , pehla wo ghulam jo Allah ka aur apney malikon ka haq ada karey , doosra wo aadmi jo kisi qom ki imaamat karey aur wo us sey razi hon, aur teesra wo aadmi jo raat aur din mein namaz key liye paanch baar bulata hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey Sufiyan Sory ki riwayat sey jantey hain, jisey wo Abul Yaqzaan sey riwayat kartey hain. 2- Abul Yaqzaan ka naam Usman bin Qais hai, unhen Usman bin Umer bhi kaha jata hai aur yehi mashhoor hai."
1987,"ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jahan bhi raho Allah sey daro, burai key baad (jo tum sey ho jaey) bhalai karo jo burai ko mita dey padhi. aur logon key sath Hasan (achchhe) akhlaq sey pesh aaoo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1988,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''bad-gumaani sey bacho, isliye ke bad-gumaani sab sey jhooti baat hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sufiyan kehtey hain ke guman do tarah ka hota hai, eik tarah ka guman gunah ka sabab hai aur eik tarah ka guman gunah ka sabab nahin hai, jo guman gunah ka sabab hai wo ye hai ke aadmi kisi key barey mein guman karey aur usey zaban par laaye, aur jo guman gunah ka sabab nahin hai wo ye hai ke aadmi kisi key barey mein guman karey aur usey zaban par na laaye."
1989,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamarey ghar walon key sath is qadr mil-jul-kar rehtey they ke hamarey chhotey bhai sey farmatey : Abu Umer ! nughair (ek tarah ki chidyaa) ka kya huwa?
1990,logon ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! aap hum sey hansi mazaq kartey hain? aap ney farmaya : ''main (khush tabae aur mazaak mein bhi) haq key siwa kuchh nahin kehta.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1991,"eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey sawari ki darkhaast ki, aap ney farmaya : ''main tumhen sawari key liye oontni ka bachcha dunga.''  us aadmi ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! main oontni ka bachcha kya karunga? Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''bhala oont ko oontni key siwa koi aur bhi janti hai?''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
1992,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney in ko mukhatib kartey huye farmaya : ''aey do kaan waley !'' Mehmood bin Ghelaan kehtey hain : abu-Usaama ney kaha , yani aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us sey mazaak kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih gharib hai."
1993,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs (jhagdey key waqt) jhoot bolnaa chhod dey halanke wo nahaq par hai, uskey liye atraafe-jannat main eik makaan banaya jaeyga, jo shakhs haq par hotey huye jhagda chhod dey uskey liye jannat key beech main eik makaan banaya jaeyga aur jo shakhs apney akhlaq achchhey banaey uskey liye aa'laa jannat main eik makaan banaya jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai, hum isey sirf Salma bin Vardaan ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey wo Anas bin Malik sey riwayat kartey hain."
1994,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tumharey liye yehi gunah kafi hai ke tum hamesha jhagadtey raho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
1995,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''apney bhai sey mat jhagdo, na us sey hansi mazaq karo, aur na us sey koi aisa wada karo jiski tum khilaf warzi karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
1996,"eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaney ki ijazat maangi, us waqt main aap key paas thi, aap ney farmaya : ''ye qom ka bura beta hai, ya qom ka bhai bura hai.''  phir aap ney us ko andar aaney ki ijazat dey di aur us sey naram guftoogu ki, jab wo nikal gaya to mainey aap sey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! aap ney to us ko bura kaha tha, phir aap ney us sey naram guftoogu ki, aap ney farmaya : ''Aaisha ! logon mein sab sey bura wo hai jiski bad zabani sey bachney key liye log usey chhod den.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1997,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''apney dost sey aetidaal aur aehtiyaat key sath dosti rakho shayad wo kisi din tumhara dushman ho jaey aur apney dushman sey aetidaal aur aehtiyaat key sath dushmani karo shayad wo kisi din tumhara dost bin jaaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- ye hadees Ayub key wastey sey dusri sanad sey bhi aai hai, Hasan bin abi Jaafar ney apni sanad sey iski riwayat ki hai, jo Ali key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tak pahunchti hai, ye riwayat bhi zaeef hai, is riwayat key silsiley mein sahih baat ye hai ke ye Ali sey mauqufan marvi (riwayat hui) hai aur ye unka apna qol hai."
1998,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jannat mein wo shakhs dakhil nahin hoga jis key dil mein raai key dane key barabar bhi takabbur (ghamand) hoga padhi. aur jahannam mein wo shakhs dakhil nahin hoga jis key dil mein raai key dane key barabar eman hoga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , ibne-Abbas , Salma bin Akwaa aur abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1999,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jannat mein wo shakhs dakhil nahin hoga jis key dil mein raai key barabar bhi takabbur (ghamand) ho, aur jahannam mein dakhil nahin hoga yani wo shakhs jis key dil mein raai key dane key barabar bhi eman ho.'' eik aadmi ney aap sey arz kiya : main ye pasand karta hun ke merey kapdey aur jootey achchhey hon? aap ney farmaya : ''beshak Allah Taala jamaal (khoobsurti) ko pasand karta hai, lekin takabbur us shakhs key andar hai jo haq ko na maane  aur logon ko haqeer aur kam-tar samjhey.'' baaz ehle-ilm is hadees : (ولا يدخل النار يعني من كان في قلبه مثقال ذرة من إيمان) ki tafseer mein kehtey hain ke iska mafhoom ye hai ke jis key dil mein zarra barabar bhi eman ho wo jahannam mein hamesha nahin rahega, abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis key dil mein zarra barabar bhi eman hoga wo jahannam sey bil-aakhir zarur nikleyga.''  kaee Tabe-een ney is aayat : (ربنا إنك من تدخل النار فقد أخزيته ( Sura Aale-Imran : 192)) ki tafseer bayan kartey huye kaha hai : aey merey rab ! tu ney jis ko jahannam mein hamesha key liye dal diya us ko zaleel aur ruswa kar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
2000,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' insan hamesha apney aap ko takabbur ( ghamand ( ki taraf ley jata hai, yahan tak ke zalimon ki fehrist mein uska naam likh diya jata hai, aur isliye usey wohi azab laahiq hota hai jo zalimon ko laahiq huwa ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2001,"log kehtey hain ke merey andar takabbur hai, halanke mainey gadhey ki sawari ki hai, moti chadar pahni hai aur bakri ka doodh doha hai aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney ye kaam kiye uskey andar bilkul takabbur nahin hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
2002,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' qiyamat key din momin key meezaan mein akhlaq Hasna sey bhari koi chiz nahin hogi aur Allah Taala be-haya aur bad-zaban sey nafrat karta hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , abu-Huraira, Anas aur Usama bin Shareek (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2003,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : '' meezaan mein rakhi janey wali chizon mein sey akhlaqe-Hasana ( achey akhlaq ( sey badh kar koi chiz wazni nahin hai, aur akhlaqe-Hasana ka hamil uski badolat rozeydaar aur namazi key darja tak pahunch jaeyga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai."
2004,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey us chiz key barey mein sawal kya gaya jo logon ko b-kasrat jannat mein dakhil keregi to aap ney farmaya : '' Allah ka dar aur achey akhlaq phir aap sey us chiz key barey mein sawal kya gaya jo logon ko b-kasrat jahannam mein dakhil keregi to aap ney farmaya : '' munh aur sharmgaah '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih gharib hai.
2005,"unhoney akhlaqe-Hasana ki khoobi bayan kartey huye kaha : akhlaqe-Hasana logon sey muskura kar milna hai, bhalai karna hai aur dusron ko takleef na dena hai."
2006,"mainey arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! eik aisa aadmi hai jis key paas sey main guzarta hun to meri ziyaafat nahin karta aur wo bhi kabhi-kabhi merey paas sey guzarta hai, kya main us sey badla lun? padhi. aap ney farmaya : ''nahin, ( balke ( uski ziyaafat karo '' , aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney merey badan par puraney kapdey dekhey to puchha , tumharey paas maal o dolat hai? mainey kaha : Allah ney mujhey har qism ka maal oont aur bakri Ata ki hai, aap ney farmaya : ''tumharey ooper is maal ka asar nazar aana chahiye ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. - « اقْرِهِ » ka maana hai tum uski ziyaafat karo « قری » ziyaafat ko kehtey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha, Jabir aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 4- abul-ahwas ka naam Auf bin Malik nazla Jasmi hai."
2007,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum log har eik key peechey dodney waley na bano yani agar log hamarey sath bhalai kerengey to hum bhi bhalai kerengey aur agar hamarey ooper zulm kerengey to hum bhi zulm kerengey, balke apney aap ko is baat par aamada karo ke agar log tumharey sath ehsan karen to tum bhi ehsan karo, aur agar bad-suluki karen to tum zulm na karo''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2008,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney kisi mareez ki iyaadat ki ya kisi deeni bhai sey mulaqat ki to us ko eik aawaz deney wala aawaz deta hai : tumhari duniyaawi o ukhrawi zindagi Mubarak ho, tumhara chalna Mubarak ho, tum ney jannat main eik ghar hasil kar liya''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 1- Hammad bin Salma ney « an Sabit an abi Raafey an abi Hurera an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » ki sanad sey is hadees ka kuch hissey riwayat kya hai."
2009,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' hayaa eman ka eik juz hai aur eman waley jannat mein jaeyngey aur be-hayaai ka talluq zulm sey hai aur zalim jahannam mein jaeyngey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar, abu-Bakra, abu-Umama aur Imran bin Husain (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2010,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' achi khaslat , ghor o khaus karna aur miyaana rawi nabuwat key chaubis hisson mein sey eik hissa hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2011,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney munzir bin aaid ashajj abdul-Qais sey farmaya : '' tumharey andar do khaslatein ( khubiyan ( aisi hain jo Allah Taala ko pasand hain : burdbaari aur ghor o fikr ki aadat. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ashajj Asri sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2012,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' soch samajh kar kaam karna aur jald bazi na karna Allah ki taraf sey hai aur jald bazi shetan ki taraf sey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- baaz muhaddeseen ney Abdul Muhin bin Abbas bin Sehal key barey mein kalam kya hai, aur hafzey key talluq sey unhen zaeef kaha hai, 3- Ashajj bin abdul-Qais ka naam munzir bin aaid hai."
2013,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jis shakhs ko naram bartaw ka hissa mil gaya, usey uski bhalai ka hissa bhi mil gaya aur jo shakhs naram bartaw key hissey sey mehroom raha wo bhalai sey bhi mehroom raha '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , Jareer bin Abdullah aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2014,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Muaz bin Jabal ko) haakim bana kar) Yamen rawana kartey waqt farmaya : '' mazloom ki dua sey daro , isliye ke uskey aur Allah key darmiyan koi parda aadey nahin aata '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas , Abu-Hurera , Abdullah bin umr aur abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2015,"mainey das saal tak Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat ki, aap ney kabhi mujhey uff tak na kaha , aur na hi merey kisi aisey kaam par jo mainey kya ho ye kaha ho : tum ney aisa kyon kya ? aur na hi kisi aisey kaam par jisey mainey na kya ho tum ney aisa kyon nahin kya, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam logon mein sab sey achey akhlaq key aadmi they, mainey kabhi koi resham , hareer ya koi chiz aap ki hatheli sey ziyada naram aur mulaaim nahin dekhi aur na kabhi mainey koi mushk ya atr aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key pasiney sey ziyada khushbudar dekhi . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha aur Bara Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2016,"mainey ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key akhlaq key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam fohsh bhale hi , bad-kalami karney waley aur bazaar mein cheekhney waley nahin they, aap burai ka badla burai sey nahin detey they, balke afw o darguzar farma detey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- abu-Adbullah Jadli ka naam abd bin abd hai, aur Abdur-Rehman bin abd bhi bayan kya gaya hai."
2017,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki biwiyon mein sey kisi par main is tarah ghairat nahin khati thi jis tarah khadeeja par ghairat khati thi jabke mainey unka zamana bhi nahin paya tha, is ghairat ki koi wajeh nahin thi siwaye iskey ke aap in ko bahut yad kartey they, aur agar aap bakri zibeh kartey to unki saheliyon ko dhoondtey aur gosht hadiya bhejtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai."
2018,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' merey nazdik tum mein sey) duniya mein) sab sey ziyada mehbub aur qiyamat key din mujh sey sab sey ziyada qarib bethney waley wo log hain jo tum mein behtareen akhlaq waley hain, aur merey nazdik tum mein) duniya mein) sab sey ziyada qabile-nafrat aur qiyamat key din mujh sey door bethney waley wo log hain jo baatuni, bina-ehtiyat bolney waley , zaban daraz aur takabbur karney waley « متفيهقون » hain'' , Sahaba ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! hamney « sarsaroon» ( baatuni) aur « متشدقون » (bila ehtiyat bolney waley ( ko to jaan liya lekin kon log hain? aap ney farmaya : '' takabbur karney waley '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, 2- baaz logon ney ye hadees (عن المبارك بن فضالة an محمد بن المنكدر an جابر an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم ولم) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai aur us mein (عن عبد ربه بن سعيد) key wasta ka zikr nahin kya, aur ye ziyada sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 4- sarsar (baatuni) ko kehtey hain : aur « متشدق » us aadmi ko kehtey hain : jo logon key sath guftgu mein badai jatatey aur fohsh kalaami kartey hain."
2019,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' momin laan-taan karney wala nahin hota hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- baaz logon ney isi sanad sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey yun riwayat ki hai ke aap ney farmaya : '' momin key liye munasib nahin hai ke wo laan-taan karney wala ho '' , ye hadees pehli hadees ki wazahat kar rahi hai."
2020,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik aadmi ney aa kar arz kiya : mujhey kuchh sikhaaiye lekin ziyada na bataiye taake main usey yad rakh sakoon, aap ney farmaya : ''ghussa mat karo''  wo kaee baar yehi sawal dohraata raha aur aap har baar kehtey rahey ''ghussa mat karo''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Saeed aur Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Sard (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadees aai hain."
2021,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs ghussa zabt kar ley halanke wo usey kar guzarney ki istataat rakhta ho, to qiyamat key din Allah Taala usey logon key samney bulaeyga aur usey ikhtiyar dega ke wo jis hoor ko chahey muntakhab kar ley.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2022,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo jawan kisi boodhey ka uskey budhapey ki wajeh sey ehtiraam kerey. to Allah Taala uskey liye aisey logon ko muqarrar farma dega jo us umr mein (yani budhapey mein) uska ehtiraam keren.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi shaikh yani Yazeed bin Bayan ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- Abu-Rijaal Ansari eik doosrey Raavi hain (aur jo Raavi is hadees mein hain wo Abu Rahaal hain)."
2023,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''peer aur Jumerat key din jannat key darwazey kholey jatey hain, Allah key sath kisi chiz ko shareek na thehraney walon ki us din maghfirat ki jati hai, siwaye unkey jinhoney baham (aapas mein) qata' talluq kiya hai, unkey barey mein kaha jata hai, un dono ko lota do yahan tak ke aapas mein suleh kar lein.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- baaz riwaayaton mein (ردوا هذين حتى يصطلحا) ''in dono ko apney haal par chhod do jab tak suleh na kar lein'' key alfaz marvi (riwayat hue) hain. 3- (muhtajreen) key maana (mutsarmeen) ''qata' talluq karney waley'' hain. 4- ye hadees isi riwayat key jaisi hai jo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai, aap ney farmaya : ''kisi musalman key liye jayez nahin ke wo apney bhai key sath teen din sey ziyada qata' talluq karey.''"
2024,"chand ansaariyon ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kuchh manga , aap ney unhen diya, unhoney phir manga , aap ney phir diya, phir farmaya : ''jo maal bhi merey paas hoga main us ko tum sey chhupa kar hergiz jama nahin rakhunga, lekin jo beniyazi zahir karega Allah Taala us ko ghani kar dega, jo sawal sey bacheyga Allah Taala us ko sawal sey mehfooz rakheyga, aur jo sabr ki tofiq maangeyga Allah Taala usey sabr ki tofiq ata kerega, kisi shakhs ko bhi sabr sey behtar aur kushada koi chiz nahin mili.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees Imam Malik sey (doosri sanad sey) « فلن أذخره عنكم » key alfaz key sath bhi aai hai, in dono ibaraton ka eik hi maana hai, yani tum logon sey main usey hergiz nahin rok erakhunga. 3- is bab mein Anas sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2025,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key din Allah ki nazar mein do rukhey shakhs sey badtar koi nahin hoga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas aur Ammar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2026,"Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) key paas sey eik aadmi guzra , un sey kaha gaya ke ye shakhs hukkaam key paas logon ki baaten pahunchata hai, to Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : ''chughal khor jannat mein nahin dakhil hoga.'' Sufiyan kehtey hain : « قتات » , padhi. « نمام » ''chughal khor'' ko kehtey hain. ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2027,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''hayaa aur kam-goi eman ki do shaakhen hain, jabke fohsh (gandi) kalaami aur kasrate kalam nifaq ki do shaakhen hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib, hum isey sirf Abu-Ghassaan Muhammad bin Mutrif hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- (عي) ka maana ''kam-goi'' (kam bolna) aur (بذاء) ka maana ''fohsh-goi'' (gande tareeqe se bolna) hai, (بيان) ka maana ''kasrate-kalam'' hai, maslan wo muaqarr-rareen jo lambi taqreeren kartey hain aur logon ki tareef mein aisi fasaahat baghaarte hain jo Allah ko pasand nahin hai."
2028,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamane mein do aadmi aaye padhi. aur unhoney taqreer ki, log un ki taqreer sun kar tajjub karney lagey , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamari taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : ''kuchh baaten jadu hoti hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ammar , ibne-Masood aur Abdullah bin Shikhkhir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
2029,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sadqa maal ko kam nahin karta, aur maaf aur darguzar karney sey aadmi ki izzat badhti hai, aur jo shakhs Allah key liye tawaazeh (mehman nawaazi) aur inkisari ikhtiyar karta hai Allah Taala uska rutba buland farma deta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abdur-Rehman bin Auf , ibne-Abbas aur abu-Kabsha Annmaari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- abu-Kabsha Annmaari ka naam umr bin Saad hai."
2030,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''zulm karna qiyamat key din tareekiyon ka sabab hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees ibne-Umar ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr , Aaisha , abu-Musa , Abu-Hurera , aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
2031,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kabhi bhi kisi khaney mein aeb nahin lagaya , jab aap ko pasand aata to kha letey nahin to chhod detey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2032,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam member par tashrif laye, buland aawaz sey pukara aur farmaya : ''aey Islam laney waley zabani logon ki jamaat unkey dilon tak eman nahin pahuncha hai ! musalmanon ko takleef mat do, in ko sharm mat dilaao aur unkey aeb na talash karo, isliye ke jo shakhs apney musalman bhai key aeb dhoondta hai, Allah Taala uska aeb dhoondta hai, aur Allah Taala jis key aeb dhoondta hai, usey ruswa aur zaleel kar deta hai, agar-che wo apney ghar key andar ho.'' Raavi (Nafey) kehtey hain : eik din ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney Khane-Kaaba ki taraf dekh kar kaha : Kaba ! tum kitni azmat waley ho ! aur tumhari hurmat kitni azeem hai, lekin Allah ki nazar mein momin (kamil) ki hurmat tujh sey ziyada azeem hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Husain bin Waqid ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- Is-haq bin Ibrahim Samarqandi ney bhi Husain bin Waqid sey isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai. 3- abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey bhi Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi jaisi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
2033,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ghalati karney waley hi burdbar (samajhdar) hotey hain aur tajarba waley hi daanaa hotey hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2034,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisey koi tohfa diya jaey phir agar usey muyassar ho to uska badla dey aur jisey muyassar na ho to wo (tohfa deney waley ki) tareef kerey. isliye ke jisney tareef ki usney uska shukriya ada kiya aur jisney nemat ko chupa liya usney nemat ki nashukri ki, aur jisney apney aap ko is chiz sey sanwaara jo wo nahin diya gaya hai, to wo jhoot key do kapdey pehan-ney waley ki tarah hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Asma binte Abu-Bakar aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- (ومن كتم فقد كفر) ka maana ye hai : usney is nemat ki nashukri ki."
2035,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis shakhs key sath koi bhalai ki gaee aur usney bhalai karney waley sey (جزاك الله خيراً) ''Allah taala tum ko behtar badla dey'' kaha, usney uski puri puri tareef kar di.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan jaiyed gharib hai, hum isey Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi key jaisi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai, mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey iskey barey mein puchha to unhoney la-ilmi ka izhar kiya. 3- Makki bin Ibrahim kehtey hain ke hum log ibne-Jurej Makki key paas they, eik maangney wala aaya aur un sey kuchh manga, ibne-Jurej ney apney khazaanchi sey kaha : usey eik Dinar dey do , khaazin ney kaha : merey paas sirf eik Dinar hai agar main usey dey dun to aap aur aap key ehal aur ayaal bhookey reh jaeyngey, ye sun kar ibne-Jurej ghussa ho gaey aur farmaya : usey Dinar dey do , hum ibne-Jurej key paas hi they ke eik aadmi unkey paas eik khat aur thaili ley kar aaya jisey unkey baaz (kuchh) doston ney bheja tha, khat mein likha tha : mainey pachas Dinar bhejey hain, ibne-Jurej ney thaili kholi aur shumar kiya to is mein ikkiyawan Dinar they, ibne-Jurej ney apney khaazin sey kaha : tum ney eik Dinar diya to Allah Taala ney tum ko usey mazeed pachas Dinar key sath lota diya."
